---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { faqs } from '../data/faq';
---

<Layout
  title="Percorsi di partnership e consulenza digitale | Bitora Piemonte"
  description="Scopri come Bitora accompagna aziende e professionisti in Piemonte con consulenze digitali su misura. Roadmap condivisa, supporto continuativo e pochi investimenti fissi: tessere NFC, sito vetrina e landing page."
>
  <section class="py-24 md:py-28">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
          Partnership digitale in Piemonte
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-5xl">
          Consulenza mirata, roadmap condivisa, supporto continuo.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Dal primo audit fino alla crescita costante: Bitora diventa il tuo partner digitale a Carmagnola, Torino e in tutto il Piemonte. Lavoriamo su strategia, design, contenuti, automazioni e visibilità su motori di ricerca e answer engine AI.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="/contattaci"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-custom-lg transition-colors hover:bg-primary-600"
          >
            Prenota la consulenza introduttiva
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/393514979670"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-primary/40 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10 dark:border-white/20 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Scrivici su WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Scoperta e insight',
            description:
              'Colloquio con i referenti, analisi della presenza digitale attuale, reputazione locale e visibilità su Google, Bing, ChatGPT e Gemini.'
          },
          {
            title: 'Blueprint operativo',
            description:
              'Roadmap con priorità condivise, proposte di investimento, KPI e timeline. Identifichiamo asset chiave: sito, landing, NFC, campagne.'
          },
          {
            title: 'Partnership attiva',
            description:
              'Sviluppo, copywriting, SEO locale e ottimizzazioni per answer engine. Report mensili e supporto diretto del team Bitora.'
          }
        ].map(({ title, description }, index) => (
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:border-primary/40 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
            <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-sm font-semibold text-white">
              {String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
            </span>
            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">{description}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Investimenti già definiti</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
          Tre acceleratori con prezzo trasparente. Tutto il resto è personalizzato.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Tessera NFC premium</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-primary">€20 <span class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500">cad.</span></p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Materiale resistente, grafica personalizzata, programmazione e landing rapida incluse.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Consegna in 5-7 giorni lavorativi</li>
            <li>• QR di backup incluso</li>
            <li>• Aggiornamenti illimitati alla landing</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sito vetrina su misura</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-primary">€500</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Fino a quattro pagine ottimizzate per mobile, SEO locale e answer engine. Design minimal, contenuti in italiano e tracciamento analytics.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Pagine extra: +€100 cad.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Landing page ad alta conversione</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-primary">€300</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Pensata per campagne mirate, con copywriting persuasivo, CTA chiare, moduli ottimizzati e misurazione lead.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Delivery entro 10 giorni lavorativi</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 rounded-3xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/10 p-6 text-center text-sm text-primary dark:border-primary/30 dark:bg-primary/20">
        Tutti gli altri servizi (ecommerce, automazioni, CRM, formazione, campagne) vengono preventivati in consulenza dopo la definizione della roadmap.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50/70 dark:bg-white/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-10 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Partnership in pratica</p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-3xl">
              Cosa ricevi collaborando con Bitora
            </h2>
          </div>
          <a href="/contattaci" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-primary/40 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10 dark:border-white/20 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/10">
            Parla con un consulente ↗
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {[
            'Un partner unico per strategia, sviluppo, contenuti e analisi',
            'Documentazione chiara: roadmap, backlog e report mensili',
            'Supporto on-demand via Slack, email e WhatsApp Business',
            'Ottimizzazioni SEO locali e answer engine optimization',
            'Testing performance e accessibilità su dispositivi reali',
            'Formazione del personale su nuovi flussi digitali'
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/60 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-primary">•</span> {item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="faq" class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Domande frequenti</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">Dubbi sulla partnership? Rispondiamo qui.</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Una selezione delle domande che riceviamo più spesso da ristoranti, hotel, professionisti e PMI piemontesi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        {faqs.slice(0, 6).map((faq, index) => (
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
            <button
              class="faq-trigger flex w-full items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 transition-colors hover:text-primary focus:outline-none dark:text-white"
              data-target={`faq-${index}`}
            >
              <span>{faq.question}</span>
              <span class="faq-icon text-primary">+</span>
            </button>
            <div id={`faq-${index}`} class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <p>{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl px-6 py-12 text-center md:px-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
          Raccontaci le tue priorità. Disegniamo insieme il percorso migliore.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Prenota una call oppure scrivici su WhatsApp: prepareremo una valutazione gratuita con esempi, tempistiche e possibili scenari di investimento.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="/contattaci"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-custom-lg transition-colors hover:bg-primary-600"
          >
            Prenota la consulenza introduttiva
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/393514979670"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-primary/40 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10 dark:border-white/20 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Scrivici su WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    const triggers = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-trigger');
    triggers.forEach(trigger => {
      trigger.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const targetId = trigger.getAttribute('data-target');
        const content = targetId ? document.getElementById(targetId) : null;
        const icon = trigger.querySelector('.faq-icon');

        if (!content || !icon) return;

        const isOpen = !content.classList.contains('hidden');
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-content').forEach(el => el.classList.add('hidden'));
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-icon').forEach(el => (el.textContent = '+'));

        if (!isOpen) {
          content.classList.remove('hidden');
          icon.textContent = '−';
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
